SUMMARY:CKUT x Queercorps x Venus – 2026 Funding Drive Benefit Concert
LOCATION:1345 Bellechasse
DESCRIPTION:2026-04-17 20:00:00\n\n1345 Bellechasse\n\nhttps://www.openstr
 eetmap.org/node/11972640567\n\nCKUT x Queercorps x Venus – 2026 Funding 
 Drive Benefit Concert\n&nbsp\;\nJoin CKUT\, Queercorps\, and Venus for an 
 intergalactic night of live music\, queer joy\, and independent radio 📡
 ✨\nWe’re broadcasting live from deep space (aka Montréal) - expect hi
 gh-volume transmissions\, cosmic noise\, and dancefloor frequencies from a
 cross the galaxy.\nFeaturing music from:\nMe\, You. Sick.\nSteeple\nBlood 
 Farts\nVitamin Pink\n📅&nbsp\;Friday\, April 17th\, 2026\n🕙&nbsp\;8:0
 0 PM – 3:00 AM\n📍&nbsp\;Parquette - 1345 Rue de Bellechasse\n💸&nbs
 p\;Tickets $20 (No one turned away for lack of funds) • https://www.zeff
 y.com/en-CA/ticketing/ckut-x-queercorps-x-venus-2026-funding-drive-show\n
 ✨ ALL AGES ✨\nDoors: 8:00pm\nShow: 9:00 – LATE\n&nbsp\;\nEvery ticke
 t helps fuel the signal.\nYour support powers grassroots\, non-corporate r
 adio and keeps queer and under-represented voices broadcasting loud and cl
 ear across every frequency.\nThis is community radio in orbit\, local arti
 sts\, real stories\, and sounds you won’t find anywhere else in the know
 n universe.\nLock in. Show up. Tune out the ordinary.\nHelp us hold space\
 , on the dancefloor and on the airwaves\, for the sounds and stories that 
 deserve to travel far.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.openstreetmap.org/node/11972640567
